# OASIS WebAPI — Implementation Queue
# Run in order. Each task must pass dotnet build + dotnet test before the next.

[1] validation-mapping-infrastructure
Goal: Add FluentValidation and AutoMapper packages, register in Program.cs, create OASISMappingProfile.
Files: OASIS.WebAPI.csproj, Program.cs, Mapping/OASISMappingProfile.cs
Acceptance: dotnet build passes, services resolve correctly.

[2] validation-mapping-avatar-validators
Goal: Create AvatarRegisterValidator, AvatarLoginValidator, AvatarUpdateValidator.
Files: Validation/AvatarRegisterValidator.cs, Validation/AvatarLoginValidator.cs, Validation/AvatarUpdateValidator.cs
Acceptance: Invalid register/login/update requests return 400 with structured errors.

[3] validation-mapping-holon-validators
Goal: Create HolonCreateValidator, HolonUpdateValidator.
Files: Validation/HolonCreateValidator.cs, Validation/HolonUpdateValidator.cs
Acceptance: Invalid holon requests return 400 with structured errors.

[4] validation-mapping-manager-refactor
Goal: Refactor AvatarManager.UpdateAsync and HolonManager.UpdateAsync to use AutoMapper.
Files: Managers/AvatarManager.cs, Managers/HolonManager.cs
Acceptance: Existing tests still pass, no regression.

[5] validation-mapping-tests
Goal: Add unit tests for validators and mapping profile.
Files: OASIS.WebAPI.Tests/Validation/*, OASIS.WebAPI.Tests/Mapping/*
Acceptance: New tests pass, Stryker score >= 50% for new code.

[6] wallet-api-interfaces
Goal: Create IWalletManager, WalletCreateModel, WalletUpdateModel, WalletQueryRequest, PortfolioResult.
Files: Interfaces/Managers/IWalletManager.cs, Models/Requests/WalletCreateModel.cs, Models/Requests/WalletUpdateModel.cs, Models/Requests/WalletQueryRequest.cs, Models/Responses/PortfolioResult.cs
Acceptance: Interfaces compile.

[7] wallet-api-manager
Goal: Implement WalletManager with CRUD, SetDefaultAsync, GetPortfolioAsync.
Files: Managers/WalletManager.cs
Acceptance: All methods call ProviderContext.Activate and delegate to IOASISStorageProvider.

[8] wallet-api-controller
Goal: Create WalletController with 7 endpoints (GET/POST/PUT/DELETE + set-default + portfolio).
Files: Controllers/WalletController.cs
Acceptance: All endpoints protected by [Authorize], ownership verified.

[9] wallet-api-provider-extensions
Goal: Add LoadAllWalletsAsync to IOASISStorageProvider and implement in EfStorageProvider + InMemoryStorageProvider.
Files: Interfaces/IOASISStorageProvider.cs, Providers/EfStorageProvider.cs, Providers/InMemoryStorageProvider.cs
Acceptance: Provider methods return correct results.

[10] wallet-api-migrate-avatar
Goal: Remove wallet methods from AvatarManager/AvatarController. Optionally keep backward-compat endpoints that delegate to WalletManager.
Files: Managers/AvatarManager.cs, Controllers/AvatarController.cs, Interfaces/Managers/IAvatarManager.cs
Acceptance: Existing wallet tests migrated or removed, no build errors.

[11] wallet-api-tests
Goal: Unit + integration tests for WalletManager and WalletController.
Files: OASIS.WebAPI.Tests/Managers/WalletManagerTests.cs, OASIS.WebAPI.IntegrationTests/Controllers/WalletControllerIntegrationTests.cs
Acceptance: Tests pass, Stryker score >= 50%.

